          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "Identity",
          "documentation": "One of: Identity | Sigmoid | Softmax | Threshold. Controls how raw circuit output is mapped to a prediction. Identity = pass-through (default). Sigmoid maps (-inf,+inf) -> (0,1). Softmax normalises a vector to a probability distribution. Threshold applies a hard cut-off at the value given by the threshold attribute."
